        together with :meth:`~sage.libs.ppl.Poly_Gen_Relation.implies`
        or :meth:`~sage.libs.ppl.Poly_Con_Relation.implies`, for
        example::

            sage: p.relation_with( x+y<1 ).implies(Poly_Con_Relation.saturates())
            True

